        <mxCell id="9c7xRbJlylDjIsSE94i9-1" value="Key notes:&lt;br&gt;- Font is Amazon Ember, 12 points for titles, 8 points for icons if needed.&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;- Icons get resized to 25x25 (and turn off their Resizable attribute) - this is their size in the AWS Groups section, but services icons tend to come in at 60x60.&lt;br&gt;- Top spacing on container boxes is -6 pt if multiline, -2 pt if single line titles&lt;br&gt;- Save images as PNG, at 150% scale, 10 pixel border, white background.&lt;br&gt;- Arrows use the 3rd option down for window head.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;- All images should fit in the &quot;Standard diagram size box&quot; below.&lt;br&gt;- Service boxes are filled with their line color, at 15% opacity&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=none;align=left;fillColor=none;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Amazon Ember;fontSize=20;" parent="1" vertex="1">
